title: 820-01814-01 not coming up
message:
the system came initially with a nand short
On pp2v5_nand_ssd0, I cleared the short and restore with configurator2. It worked and sent out for deliver. After a week it was returned dead and I discovered another short on ppbus_g3h_ssd0_sns, I cleared it. Configurator2 successfully restored it ( the padlock logo came on the other laptop but the system in question has no display nothing. Still dead. Pls what to do
